programme.title: Pembancuh Kopi Mr Vampire Ep30
programme.desc: Nuzul tiba di hadapan Teratak Ayuni. Pertama kali tiba di rumah tersebut, Nuzul kagum dengan keindahan rumah agam itu. Dia membawa sekeping fail yang memerlukan tandatangan seseorang dengan cepat. Nuzul mahu pulang namun dia bertembung dengan Puan Sri Ayuni dan Nuzul diminta untuk makan tengahari di situ. Semasa makan tengahari, Puan Sri Ayuni mengambil peluang untuk berkenalan dengan Nuzul dan bertanya tentang keluarganya. Nuzul perasan ada yang sedang memerhatikannya dan itu membuatkan dia tidak selesa. Sejurus selepas itu, Irsyad yang juga baru muncul di café tersebut memanggil Nuzul. Irsyad menulis nota supaya Nuzul jangan menggatal dengan pelanggan. Nuzul sentap. Nuzul pelik dengan sikap Irsyad yang mudah berubah-ubah. Sejak itu Nuzul menggelarkan Irsyad, “Mr. Vampire.”

programme.desc: Salina@ Sally cuba pertahankan Hisyam tetapi Tn Rahim terlalu ego untuk mengubah keputusannya. Dr Rohaya memaklumkan Maya sudah kesuntukan masa dan perlukan pembedahan segera. Hisyam resah wang masih belum cukup melainkan terpaksa menjual kembali galerinya kepada Zarif. Daniel terkejut kerana dulu Hisyam beriya-iya mahukan galeri sehingga Maya datang merayu kepadanya. Dia menyindir jika dulu Maya berkahwin dengan Zarif, mungkin nasib hidupnya tidak seteruk sekarang. Maya beritahu dia tidak menyesal dan bahagia dengan Hisyam. Daniel juga beritahu Hisyam mahu jual galeri itu semula untuk tanggung kos rawatan Maya. Maya menjerit menghalaunya keluar dari situ. Lebih-lebih lagi melihat Syifa mengambil alih tugasnya membuat dan menjual kek batik kerana mahu membantu Papanya. Hisyam nasihatkan Maya harus bertahan untuk terus hidup kerana anak-anak masih perlukannya. programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep16
programme.desc: Memaparkan Shariff terus meminati Hani dia memujuk Yusri untuk menceritakan sejauh mana hal Hani. Dalam masa yang sama Shariff ada masalah keluarga berpunca bapanya. Dia juga akui kepada Dzul dan pernah menghubungi Hani untuk temujanji, tetapi Hani tegas menolak. Nizam yang baru bekerja di Johor Bahru menerima kunjungan mengejut Sheila. Di peringkat mula Nizam bukan sahaja memarahi Sheila tetapi tidak mahu menerima kedatangan dan melayannya. Dia juga mengherdik dengan kata-kata kesat. Sehingga Sheila merayu agar memberi ruang dan peluang akhirnya terbuka juga hati Nizam. Lantaran itu, Sheila berkesempatan memberi tahu secara serius kepada Nizam bahawa Mizan amat sayangkan Hani dan lupakan sahaja hasratnya. Setakat ini Nizam masih tidak percaya. Apa pun dia juga menyatakan kepada Sheila dia akan mencari rumah mereka di Johor Bahru dan meminta Sheila pulang. Mizan delima kerana membayangkan keadaan yang amat tidak sesuai berlaku jika Sharif rakan baiknya menghawini Hani dan mereka pula sepejabat. Dalam pada itu Suraya pula cuba mengapi-apikan rumah tangganya. Antara Mizan dengan Hani masih dingin, tetapi Hani lebih tenang dan masing-masing tidak abaikan tanggungjawab rumah tangga.

programme.title: Baby Tak Gila Ep07
programme.desc: Baby pula beria nak ambil hati Akram. Dia cuba masak untuk Akram. Masak pelik-pelik tak masuk akal, sebelum ni mana pernah masak? Ini tiber!. Buatkan air untuk Akram lah, dessert lah macam-macam lagi Baby buat untuk beli jiwa Akram. Akram cuba siasat siapa Baby ni?Antasia dan Dato Alin berjumpa. Konon dia fikir yang Dato Alin nak menjodohkan dia dengan Akram, padahal dia bakal dibodohkan oleh Dato Alin, sebab Dato Alin nak tanya pasal Baby lebih dekat.

programme.desc: Tn Rahim berasa puas hati, Sumayah@ Maya dan cucu-cucunya kini berada bersamanya dan baginya Hisyam telah tewas kerana kekayaaan mengatasi segala-galanya. Maya sering teringatkan saat-saat manis bersama suaminya itu, begitu juga Hisyam yang tidak mampu berbuat apa-apa. Tok Daddy cuba ambil hati Haikal dan adakan majlis sambutan harijadinya. Dia perlukan sokongan orang yang paling dicintai. Pn Mahani acapkali menasihati Tn Rahim agar mengetepikan status dan ego kerana tidak sanggup melihat keperitan Maya. Salina@ Sally beritahu ibunya tentang rancangan Tn Rahim memisahkan Hisyam dan Maya. Suatu hari, Hisyam datang ke rumah Tn Rahim setelah dipujuk Pn Mahani tempoh hari, memberitahu tentang kemurungan Maya. Haikal dan Syifa yang rindukan Hisyam menerpa dan memeluknya. Pn Mahani sudah tidak tahan lagi dengan sikap ego suaminya sehingga sanggup membuat orang lain menderita. Dia berterus-terang bahawa dia tahu suaminya yang merancang memisahkan Hisyam dan Maya setelah bersetuju membiayai kos rawatan Maya. Tn Rahim mahu Hisyam dilihat suami yang jahat. Kemudian, Maya melutut pada Tn Rahim, merayu agar kasihankan dirinya yang sedang sakit dan menerima Hisyam. Kata-kata Maya dan Hisyam membuatkan Tn Rahim tersentuh lalu mengalirkan air mata sekaligus membuang egonya yang kian lama terpahat. Tn Rahim melihat kegembiraan diwajah Maya dan cucu-cucunya setelah bertemu Hisyam dan mereka saling berpelukan. Dia akhirnya kesal dengan sikap egonya selama ini. Hisyam dan Maya akhirnya mengecapi bahagia yang kekal abadi dan kali ini lebih bererti dengan restu dari keluarga.

programme.desc:
SETAHUN YANG LALU. Mona masih menetap bersama ibu bapanya. Ibu bapanya cuba mencari calon suami untuknya, namun, dengan bantuan kawan baiknya, Mimi Kirana, Mona menolak lamaran mereka dengan pelbagai helah.
Fareez berpindah masuk ke rumah sebelah dan menjadi jiran Mona. Bermula dengan salah faham, hubungan Fareez dan Mona menjadi semakin rapat, sehingga disalah anggap dan menjadi perbualan orang di sekitar. Ibu bapa Mona mula menaruh pandangan negatif terhadap Fareez. Mona dipaksa memutuskan hubungan dengannya. Namun, Fareez nekad mengharungi pelbagai dugaan demi mengahwini Mona, sehingga ibu bapa Mona akhirnya mengalah dan bersetuju.
Sehari sebelum perkahwinan mereka, Fareez mati kemalangan ketika cuba menunaikan permintaan Mona. Perkahwinan terbatal. Mona hidup dalam trauma.

programme.title: Cinta Tanpa Henti Ep19
programme.desc: Hisyam buntu, Tn Rahim meletakkan syarat yang berat untuk membeli galeri itu. Salina@ Sally bertemu Maya dan minta maaf padanya, dia berusaha kembali ke pangkal jalan. Hisyam tidak tahu bagaimana akan melalui hari-hari mendatang tanpa Maya nanti. Hisyam cuba sembunyikan hal itu dari Maya, Hisyam mengingatkan kepada Maya saat-saat percintaan mereka. Maya hairan dengan kata-kata Hisyam.Tn Rahim mahu bawa Maya ke luar negara untuk segerakan lakukan transplan hati Maya kerana masih belum ada penderma. Oleh itu, Hisyam mesti berjanji pada Tn Rahim untuk melepaskan Maya jika mahu Maya selamat. Sebulan kemudian, pemindahan hati Maya berjaya dilakukan. Maya terus dibawa pulang ke rumah Daddynya, dia tertanya-tanya tentang Hisyam yang langsung tidak mencarinya, begitu juga anak-anaknya. Walhal, Hisyam sangat merindui Maya tetapi terikat dengan janjinya. Maya terlalu rindukan mereka dan pulang ke rumah untuk dapatkan jawapan dari Hisyam. Hisyam terpaksa berbohong bahawa Maya hanya membebankannya. Bagaikan luluh hati Maya dengan kata-kata Hisyam, dia akur dan meninggalkan Hisyam, membawa anakanaknya sekali. Hisyam menitiskan air mata terpaksa hidup dalam pembohongan itu.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep17
programme.desc: Memaparkan Hani masih bersedih kerana Mizan seperti tidak menerimanya. Sedang Hani duduk di sebuah kedai minum, kebetulan Suraya nampaknya, tanpa diundang dia mengapi-apikan Hani. Pilihan terbaik hanya bercerai Mizan demi keselamatan dan kebahagiaan ibu bapanya dan Nizam akan buat apa saja. Hani beredar dan ke kedai lain, kebetulan Shariff datang ke kedai itu menegurnya yang masih bersedih. Hani berbual dengan Shariff atas dasar rakan dan "client", perniagaan Hani secara on line. Hani menerima pelawaan Shariff untuk menghantarnya pulang. Nizam mengetahui lalu marah dan amat cemburu dan sekali lagi mengulangi serta bertegas akan mengahwininya juga. Semuanya menambah kekusutan Hani. Selepas bersembahyang Hani berdoa seperti kebiasaannya. Sebelah malamnya, Mizan kelihatan positif membuatkan Hani lega. Sementara itu, ibu dan bapa mereka bersama Sheila dalam perjalanan ke rumah mereka. Kedatangan mereka kerana ingin melawat ibu dan bapa Sheila kemalangan. Sebelum itu Nizam tiba dahulu di rumah mereka bagi tujuan yang sama. Semasa Mizan menyiapkan bilik ibu dan bapanya termasuk membawa barang Hani ke biliknya (Hani dan Mizan masih tidur di bilik berasingan), Nizam berkesempatan memujuk rayu Hani lagi, malahan rancangannya, Sheila akan diceraikan. Hani sentiasa mengalih perbualan Nizam sehingga mengatakan dia telah mengandung. Hani dan Mizan juga bertingkah laku begitu mesra kepada Nizam sekali gus terhadap ibu bapa mereka.

programme.title: Baby Tak Gila Ep08

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep17
programme.desc: Memaparkan Hani masih bersedih kerana Mizan seperti tidak menerimanya. Sedang Hani duduk di sebuah kedai minum, kebetulan Suraya nampaknya, tanpa diundang dia mengapi-apikan Hani. Pilihan terbaik hanya bercerai Mizan demi keselamatan dan kebahagiaan ibu bapanya dan Nizam akan buat apa saja. Hani beredar dan ke kedai lain, kebetulan Shariff datang ke kedai itu menegurnya yang masih bersedih. Hani berbual dengan Shariff atas dasar rakan dan "client", perniagaan Hani secara on line. Hani menerima pelawaan Shariff untuk menghantarnya pulang. Nizam mengetahui lalu marah dan amat cemburu dan sekali lagi mengulangi serta bertegas akan mengahwininya juga. Semuanya menambah kekusutan Hani. Selepas bersembahyang Hani berdoa seperti kebiasaannya. Sebelah malamnya, Mizan kelihatan positif membuatkan Hani lega. Sementara itu, ibu dan bapa mereka bersama Sheila dalam perjalanan ke rumah mereka. Kedatangan mereka kerana ingin melawat ibu dan bapa Sheila kemalangan. Sebelum itu Nizam tiba dahulu di rumah mereka bagi tujuan yang sama. Semasa Mizan menyiapkan bilik ibu dan bapanya termasuk membawa barang Hani ke biliknya (Hani dan Mizan masih tidur di bilik berasingan), Nizam berkesempatan memujuk rayu Hani lagi, malahan rancangannya, Sheila akan diceraikan. Hani sentiasa mengalih perbualan Nizam sehingga mengatakan dia telah mengandung. Hani dan Mizan juga bertingkah laku begitu mesra kepada Nizam sekali gus terhadap ibu bapa mereka.

programme.title: Cinta Tanpa Henti Ep20
programme.desc: Tn Rahim berasa puas hati, Sumayah@ Maya dan cucu-cucunya kini berada bersamanya dan baginya Hisyam telah tewas kerana kekayaaan mengatasi segala-galanya. Maya sering teringatkan saat-saat manis bersama suaminya itu, begitu juga Hisyam yang tidak mampu berbuat apa-apa. Tok Daddy cuba ambil hati Haikal dan adakan majlis sambutan harijadinya. Sebaliknya, Haikal memberontak kerana rindukan papanya dan mahu papanya turut serta. Kesihatan Maya berambah buruk dan menurut doktor Maya kemurungan kerana tertekan. Dia perlukan sokongan orang yang paling dicintai. Pn Mahani acapkali menasihati Tn Rahim agar mengetepikan status dan ego kerana tidak sanggup melihat keperitan Maya. Salina@ Sally beritahu ibunya tentang rancangan Tn Rahim memisahkan Hisyam dan Maya. Suatu hari, Hisyam datang ke rumah Tn Rahim setelah dipujuk Pn Mahani tempoh hari, memberitahu tentang kemurungan Maya. Haikal dan Syifa yang rindukan Hisyam menerpa dan memeluknya. Pn Mahani sudah tidak tahan lagi dengan sikap ego suaminya sehingga sanggup membuat orang lain menderita. Dia berterus-terang bahawa dia tahu suaminya yang merancang memisahkan Hisyam dan Maya setelah bersetuju membiayai kos rawatan Maya. Tn Rahim mahu Hisyam dilihat suami yang jahat. Kemudian, Maya melutut pada Tn Rahim, merayu agar kasihankan dirinya yang sedang sakit dan menerima Hisyam. Kata-kata Maya dan Hisyam membuatkan Tn Rahim tersentuh lalu mengalirkan air mata sekaligus membuang egonya yang kian lama terpahat. Tn Rahim melihat kegembiraan diwajah Maya dan cucu-cucunya setelah bertemu Hisyam dan mereka saling berpelukan. Dia akhirnya kesal dengan sikap egonya selama ini. Hisyam dan Maya akhirnya mengecapi bahagia yang kekal abadi dan kali ini lebih bererti dengan restu dari keluarga.

programme.title: Perang Bibir Ep04
programme.desc: Plot cerita ini berdasarkan kehidupan kugiran Rimba Bara setelah Zack mengambil keputusan untuk berundur dari kumpulan tersebut. Cerita bermula dengan kisah bagaimana Amy Mat Piah melalui hari-harinya selepas dibuang dari kumpulan Rimba Bara. Hari-hari beliau sering dihantui dengan kisah Rimba Bara, walaupun beliau telah meneruskan pekerjaan beliau sebagai pembuat air batu campur. Pada masa yang sama Rimba Bara dikejutkan dengan perkhabaran tentang penyanyi utama mereka, Zul Kapan yang menghadiri uji bakat yang dilakukan oleh Syarikat rakaman milik M. Nasir, Luncai Emas. Berita tersebut telah sampai ke pengetahuan Amy dan kesempatan tersebut cuba diambil untuk merapati semula kumpulan lama yang pernah dianggotainya. Zul Kapan dan Lan Lentik meninggalkan Rimba Bara selepas Luncai Emas bersetuju untuk mengambil Kumpulan Malaikat Maut sebagai artis rakaman. Kebuntuan mencari ahli baru selesai apabila mereka mengambil Slash untuk menggantikan Lan lentik sebagai gitaris utama manakala Amy telah diberi peluang kedua sebagai penyanyi utama.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep18
programme.desc: Memaparkan semua keluarga Hani ada di rumahnya. Nizam mahu tidak mahu terpaksa menerima Sheila dan anaknya tidur sebilik. Sementara itu hubungan Hani dan Mizan yang mesra seperti bukan berlakon lagi. Dalam pada itu Nizam tetap menyukai Hani dan Hani tahu mengelak dan berbalas cakapnya. Mereka sekeluarga juga ke hospital. Di hospital, hubungan Nizam dan Sheila masih tegang. Nizam berterus terang dia hanya berlakon jika berjumpa dengan ibu Sheila kerana dia akan berkahwin dengan Hani dan Sheila tetap akan diceraikan. Demi untuk nampak tenang, Sheila mengalah, sanggup terima apa yang dihajat Nizam. Walau pun begitu dia meminta masa. Sheila melawat ibunya di wad, walau pun dia berkata-kata telah berkahwin dan memohon maaf tetapi ibunya tidak sedar ketika itu. Sheila juga bersemuka sekali lagi dengan Hani dan terang-terang Hani menafikan segala hasrat Nizam dan didengari Nizam. Sementara itu Shariff tetap menyukai Hani dan meminta bantuan ibu saudaranya Umairah isteri Datuk Fuad menjadi wakilnya agar Hani kelak menjadi isterinya. Dalam masa yang sama Datuk Fuad, suami Umairah curang telah mengamalkan rasuah membolehkan Ah Meng mudah perolehi tender sepatutnya diperolehi syarikat mereka. Semuanya gara-gara Suraya. Berikutan itu Shariff diminta Umairah utamakan menyelamatkan syarikat mereka. Umairah juga memaklumkan Shariff berdasarkan biodata Hani, Hani itu adalah adik kandungnya.

Zafuan nampak tak senang lalu nasihatkan Aidid supaya terus-terang dengan Suzan. Tapi Haryati rancang yang lebih jahat bila dia sengaja hantar kad undangan kahwin Aidid-Juliana ke email Sy Kamariah. programme.title: Mumun
programme.desc: Mumun dan Juned adalah pasangan yang saling menyayangi. Walau bagaimanapun, Mumun meninggal dunia dalam satu kemalangan dan Juned sangat kecewa dengannya.

programme.title: You Saka..Pergi Jauh-jauh S1 Ep9
programme.desc: Episod ke 9 ini memaparkan antara lain Ibrahim hidup secara geladangan setelah lari dari Zeti. Zeti masih berusaha melalui perbomohan ingin mempengaruhi agar Datin Salina terus mempercayai kemampuannya bermotifkan kewangan. Fauzan menjadi tidak normal asyik menyebut 'Nia' dan setelah Zeti termaklum, dia sanggup mengubati, asalkan dibayar RM50,000 dan kebetulan rawatannya cara pemujaan mujarab. Secara diam-diam Zeti juga menabur sesuatu di halaman rumah Ibrahim. Sementara itu Ibrahim balik semula ke pangkuan keluarganya. Nia yang bakal menjadi menantunya dan Shasa juga bermautautin di situ. Ibrahim yang menyedari ada bahan taburan telah berusaha membuat pendinding. ementara itu, Zeti terasa panas dan gelisah dan di badannya ada tumpuk-tumpuk hitaman akhirnya lembaga hitam berjalur hijau meresapi tubuhnya. Dalam pada itu pula Datin Salina dan anaknya diganggui kemunculan lembaga putih di rumahnya. Seterusnya Ibrahim, Roslan dan Pak Abas berbincang tentang Gelam yang sering mengusik manusia dan memikir cara untuk menghindarinya. Tidak semena-mena Shasa berubah tingkahlaku 'berpakaian dan bertingkahlaku amalan 'punk' dan tidak syak lagi telah dirasuk syaitan.

programme.title: The Secret Suster Ngesot Urban
programme.desc: Mengetahui bahawa bapanya telah berkahwin dengan seorang wanita sebayanya, Kanaya meninggalkan rumah, hanya untuk mengalami kemalangan yang menyebabkan dia di hospital berhantu.

programme.title: Mantera Anjasmoro Ep12
programme.desc: Episod ini mengisahkan Zahid banyak berubah, dia terlalu menurut kata-kata Sabrina dan dia selalu menghadapi kesakitan. Ibubapa melihat kesihatan Zahid semakin merosok dan hendak menjemput ustaz Kalam merawat Zahid, tetapi Sabrina tidak mengizinkan. Zahid dimasukkan ke hospital dan doktor mengesan Zahid mengalami kerosakan organ dalaman. Anak kecil nampak hantu didalam bilik ketika menziarahi Zahid. Sabrina sendiri risau keadaan Zahid, tetapi apabila bertemu, Ramona mengatakan Sabrina tidak boleh berpatah balik kerana telah berjanji dengan sihir.

programme.title: Amukan Pocong S1 Ep4
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Awang berpuas hati kerana 2 mangsa sudah berjaya dikorbankan. Long Hussain yang masih segar dan bertenaga berjaya dipergunakan Awang dengan baik. Bila Awang mengesan mangsanya, roh Awang akan bersatu dengan jasad Long Hussain. Kali ini mangsanya adalah Mira, seorang usahawan andaman dan butik perkahwinan yang bekerja sendiri di rumah. Mira tinggal dengan kedua orang tuanya sementara adik beradiknya yang lain di Kuala Lumpur. Ketika orang tua Mira ke Kuala Lumpur Mira tinggal bersendirian. Mira diserang dan dibunuh oleh pocong.

programme.title: Chikaro
programme.desc: Mengisahkan seorang gadis kampung naif yang datang ke bandar untuk mencari pekerjaan di sebuah pejabat dan di situ dia telah bertemu dengan bekas mat rempit yang telah jatuh cinta pada pandangan pertama. Dia berusaha untuk menolong gadis itu sesuaikan diri dengan gaya hidup bandar dan akhirnya gadis kampung itu juga telah jatuh cinta kepadanya. Walaubagaimanapun kerana sifatnya yang matang, ramai wanita mencemburuinya.

programme.title: Dendam Sarakit S1 Ep6
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Haris, pengganti Rafiq, dijumpai mati akibat kemalangan di jalan raya. Kerana ini, Rafiq tidak perlu berpindah ke Kuala Lumpur. Dina yang menyerupai Sarakit dapat juga melihat apa Sarakit lalui seperti semasa Sarakit dirogol dan mempunyai perasaan benci terhadap Pak Bado. Pak Bado terus diganggu suara bayi menangis dan menjumpai janin di kebunnya. Sementara itu, Tat, salah seorang yang merogol Sarakit, mulai diganggu hantu tenggek sehingga dia tidak berani keluar malam. Ramdi berjumpa Tat untuk mengajaknya berpindah ke Kuala Lumpur kerana tidak mahu mereka mati sia-sia seperti yang berlaku pada Kiol. Tat keberatan tetapi Ramdi bersedia membawanya keluar dari kampung apabila perlu.

programme.title: Amukan Pocong S1 Ep8
programme.desc: Episod mengisahkan Tok Sayut, Sulaiman dan penghulu bermesyuarat untuk menyelesaikan masalah pocong ini. programme.desc: Episod ke 10 ini memaparkan antara lain Ibrahim, Nia dan Adrus mencari Shasa dan akhirnya dapat menemuinya dalam keadaan bertelingkahlaku dan mengamal budaya kelompok 'punk' yang diapit dan dibawa lari oleh Zeti yang memiliki dan mengamalkan budaya yang diresapi oleh Gelam. Mereka gagal menyelamatkan Shasa, sebaliknya Adrus dicederakan dan dirasuk oleh Zeti hingga tidak sedar diri. Dalam pada itu Gelam terus menemui Zeti dan mereka bertelingkah gara-gara Gelam tidak puas hati tindakannya. Dalam kekusutan Nia, semasa dia ke bandar tiba-tiba menemui Tok Alai. Dalam hubungan ini, tepat pada masanya di mana dengan bantuannya dia menasihati Ibrahim serta ahli keluarga yang lain tentang cara-cara berusaha untuk mengubati penyakit Adrus berlandaskan Islam. Nia yang berkelebihan dalam usahanya berfikir telah diberi petunjuk lokasi Shasa dan akhirnya bersama Ibrahim dan bantuan Tok Alai, Shasa berjaya diselamatkan dari rumah Zeti. Adrus masih tidak sedarkan diri

Apabila kerajaan Thai mengumumkan rancangan untuk mengosongkan bilik kebalnya untuk membayar balik pinjaman IMFnya, sekumpulan Mafia tempatan membuat satu skim untuk rompakan mega, mereka akan mencuri rizab emas negara. Mereka mengupah Navin yang terkenal, bekas pembunuh tentera, untuk mengetuai operasi yang melibatkan semua pencuri terkemuka di negara ini.

programme.title: Plan B Ep5
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Khai kalah dalam perlumbaan kereta "drift". Dia tidak mampu membayar wang taruhan sebanyak RM50 ribu lalu mengadai kereta lumbanya. Di rumah Khai terperangkap ketika dia cuba membuka peti besi wang bapanya. Dia dihalau dari rumah. Kemudian Khai berjaya meminjam wang daripada rakannya, Mica dan menebus kembali keretanya yang tergadai itu. Khai tidak pulang ke rumah hanya tidur dalam kereta yang dipakirnya di tepi jalanraya.

programme.title: You Saka..Pergi Jauh-jauh S1 Ep2
programme.desc: Episod ke 2 mengisahkan ketika Nia berada di rumah bomoh Ibrahim dia sugul kerana sebelah malamnya dia diganggui oleh saka Gelam. Kemudiannya dia mendapat panggilan memaklumkan ibunya telah meninggal dunia. Dia pulang bersama Adrus dan seterusnya membincangkan dengan Pak Lang dan Pak Abas tentang kematian dan rancangan membuat tahlil. Kemudiannya majikannya mengetahui berita kematian itu dan memutuskan akan biaya kenduri arwah. Semasa kenduri arwah lembaga putih muncul, menyebabkan jadi gempar, tetapi Datin Salina yang berada di tepi lembaga itu tidak nampak apa-apa. Sewaktu Datin balik difahamkan lembaga putih mengekorinya. Di rumah Datin, lembaga putih hanya mengganggui anaknya Fauzan. Di siang hari Fauzan terasa seorang anak gadis cantik dikenali sebagai Rosserita melayaninya dengan berbual-bual di pengkarangan rumah. Ini membuatkan Datin mula kehairanan terhadap anaknya yang berubah perangai. Ini termasuk bersikap negatif semasa makan walau pun sebagai kali pertama menemui dan bersama Nia.

programme.title: UC 5
programme.desc: Salih ditembak dengan senapang di hutan tempat dia pergi berburu bersama rakannya Metin. Salih, yang terpaksa hidup dengan peluru di otaknya, memerlukan bantuan material dan rohani untuk sembuh. Metin, yang mengatakan bahawa dia akan melakukan semua jenis bantuan kepada Salih pada mulanya. Kemudian bertunang dengan teman wanita Salih iaitu Sermin, meninggalkan Salih dengan ibunya sendirian. Arzu, bekas tunang Metin, tidak dapat memahami apa yang berlaku. Semasa cuba mencari tahu mengapa Metin berkelakuan sedemikian, Salih dan ibunya, seorang wanita luar biasa, melawat Türkan.

Malam itu adalah malam bonus buat Long Husin kerana Dila dan rakan sekhemahnya, Noy tidur bersama. Dila dan Noy menyangkakan rakan lelaki lain sengaja hendak menakutkan mereka tetapi ketia mereka nyenyak tidur, khemah mereka dibuka dan seorang demi seorang Dila dan Noy dibawa pergi. programme.title: Sangkar
programme.desc: Adam dan Johan merupakan atlet sukan bela diri campuran (MMA). Adam bersikap angkuh dan telah menang sebuah pertarungan dengan taktik kotornya. Mereka ialah musuh dan selalu bersaing. Suatu hari, apabila dicabar di luar sangkar, Adam secara tidak sengaja mencederakan Johan. Johan tercedera parah dan ahli keluarganya hilang punca rezeki dan harapan. Untuk menebus kesalahannya, Adam kembali bertarung di pertarungan bawah tanah untuk mendapatkan habuan supaya dapat membantu Johan sekeluarga. Johan pula sedang bertarung dengan kesihatan dan pemulihan demi keluarganya. Pada saat ini, Adam mengingatkan tujuan diri sebagai pejuang MMA dan mengambil cabaran untuk berlawan dengan pejuang MMA antarabangsa.

Sementara itu Zeti dengan keadaan rasukan syaitan menyeru dari rumahnya terhadap Adrus. Tatkala keluarga sedang merancang untuk rawatan Adrus, tiba-tiba Adrus hilang dari tempat baringnya. Kini dia di bawah kawalan Zeti. Dalam pada itu Tok Alai memutuskan Nia seseorang yang dapat menangkis perbuatan Gelam melalui Zeti. Bagi Datin Salina pula dia mengalami kerugian teruk perniagaan syarikatnya. Setelah mendapat nasihat dari peguamnya dia cuba memujuk Nia kembali bekerja, tetapi Nia menolaknya. Sementara itu, ketika semua ahli keluarga sedang menumpukan perhatian kepada Pak Lang tidak sedar diri kerana terkejut dan mengelak dari satu kemalangan, tiba-tiba Adrus tiba balik ke pangkuan mereka, akan tetapi tingkahlakunya berubah termasuk cara dia berkomunikasi dengan cara tidak menentu, agresif dan seolah-olah separuh waras. Berikutan itu Ibrahim bertindak mengikatnya.

programme.title: Mumun
programme.desc: Mumun dan Juned adalah pasangan yang saling menyayangi. Walau bagaimanapun, Mumun meninggal dunia dalam satu kemalangan dan Juned sangat kecewa dengannya.

programme.title: Plan B Ep6
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Khai dan Mika cuba berlatih menembak beberapa sasaran ke arah botol dari pistol yang dicuri oleh Mika milik ayahnya dan dia merancang untuk merompak syarikat ayahnya. Sementara itu Dr. Rizman cuba berbincang dengan isteri mengenai anak tunggalnya, Khai, setelah dia mendapati Khai sudah tersasar jauh daripada keluarga. Dr.Rizman juga mengakui dia telah mengabaikan tanggung jawabnya terhadap Khai. Namun Khai menolak segala bentuk bantuan daripada kedua-dua ibu bapanya, walaupun ibunya mengakui kesilapan mereka yang lalu. Kemudian Khai tidak dapat menerima hakikat, kenapa ibu bapanya bersikap demikian terhadapnya dan merasakan seolah-olah dia bukan anak kepada ayahnya, Dr.Rizman.

programme.title: Muzium Misteri Ep7
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Bad pada mulanya bersiar-siar dan Nur, anaknya pula memesan ayam golek. Bad singgah di Kg. Paling Sweet, di gerai Leman dan membeli ayam golek. Dari Leman maklumat tentang lembaga Senyum diperolehi. Encik Bad berminat dengan kisah itu, setelah mendapat maklumat lanjut dia telah mengarahkan ketiga-tiga pekerjanya supaya mendapat maklumat selanjutnya dari Leman. Yang penting misi mereka menangkap lembaga Senyum. Adam, Daniel dan Shah telah ditunjukkan rumah asal lembaga Periang, bapa lembaga Senyum. Selain itu Leman menceritakan serba ringkas latar belakang lembaga Periang dan beberapa mangsa pernah diganggu oleh lembaga senyum. Berikutan itu Adam, Shah dan Daniel telah masuk ke kawasan kampung itu dengan kereta lengkap dengan peralatan serta keupayaan mereka untuk memerangkap lembaga senyum. Sementara itu Nur terus menjadi tali penghubung di antara bapa dan ibunya. Bapanya menerima kiriman ibunya, tetapi menunjukkan tidak berapa suka. Waktu lapang, Shah akan menghubungi dengan kekasihnya melalui khidmat pesanan ringkas. Pun begitu tetap merahsiakan kepada Adam.

programme.title: Tom Yum Goong
programme.desc: Tom yum goong (2005) ialah filem Thai,Inggeris,Mandarin,Vietnam. Prachya Pinkaew telah mengarahkan filem ini. Tony Jaa,Nathan Jones,Xing Jin,Petchtai Wongkamlao adalah pelakon filem ini. Ia telah dikeluarkan pada tahun 2005. Tom yum goong (2005) dianggap sebagai salah satu filem Aksi, Jenayah, Drama, Thriller terbaik di India dan di seluruh dunia.

programme.title: Gila - Gila Pengantin
programme.desc: Aliah seorang gadis yang ingin berkahwin tetapi mempunyai satu fobia dimana dia takut untuk bersanding dia atas pelamin setelah apa yang terjadi keatas dirinya semasa dia kecil. Dalam masa yang sama, Johari juga mempunyai masalah yang sama dengan Aliah. Mereka telah bertemu di dalam dunia cyber dan beramah mesra dengan perbualan masing-masing sehingga hari ini. Rupa-rupanya ada kenangan di antara mereka berdua. Namun mereka bakal berkahwin dengan pasangan yang berlainan dari mereka dan kedua-duanya perlu bersanding di atas pelamin ketika majlis perkahwinan.

programme.title: XX Ray 2
programme.desc: Bekerja sebagai saintis kadet, Tina berasa ditipu apabila Johan mendakwa dia yang mencipta mesin pelupusan laser walhal ia merupakan hasil cetusan idea dari Tina. Ingin menghalang niat jahat Johan, Tina meminta bantuan Amir. Namun, keduanya terkena pancaran laser mesin itu dalam cubaan untuk menghalang Johan dan telah dihantar ke zaman Kesultanan Melayu Melaka.

programme.title: Scoop
programme.desc: Tania, seorang wartawan menjalankan penyiasatan tentang kes pembunuhan rakannya, Johari yang menyiasat skandal syarikat kewangan. Skandal tersebut melibatkan bapa Sheila. Dibantu oleh seorang jurufoto, Norman yang ingin membersihkan namanya kerana sebelum Johari mati dibunuh, terdapat pertengkaran antara mereka berdua. Mereka pun mula menyiasat punca sebenar pembunuhan Johari.

programme.title: Gila - Gila Pengantin Remaja
programme.desc: Pasangan remaja yang bakal menduduki peperiksaan SPM, Amir dan Mastura berikrar ingin berkahwin selepas tamatnya pengajian di universiti. Namun, Fandi yang juga rakan sekelas Mastura mencemburui percintaan mereka. SPM pun tiba tetapi Mastura terlewat menghadiri ujian Matematik dan berasa amat kecewa kerana menganggap dia telah pun gagal. Kakak Mastura, Anita pula ingin Mastura mencari calon suami yang kaya. Perasaan kecewa mula menyelubungi diri Amir apabila mendapat tahu Mastura ditunangkan dengan Fandi. Mengetahui perihal sebenar mengapa mereka akan dikahwinkan, Amir membawa Mastura lari ke selatan Thailand. Bermulalah kekecohan antara mereka semua dalam sekuel kepada Gila-Gila Pengantin ini.

programme.title: Femina
programme.desc: Perjuangan untuk mendapatkan hak setara antara jantina terutamanya wanita lantang dibicarakan di dalam majalah Femina. Tina, tegas memperjuangkan pendiriannya manakala Anita tidak berapa menyukai cara Tina. Femina telah menjadi satu platform anti-lelaki. Pertemuan Tina bersama Pyan mula mengubah pandangan ekstrem Tina namun perasaan dilema mula menguasai diri apabila dituduh sebagai pembelot wanita.

programme.title: Bukan Cinta Malaikat
programme.desc: Reyhan, seorang sukarelawan Muslim Care yang berasal dari Bandung jatuh hati kepada gadis Malaysia bernama Dewi sejak dia menyelamatkan Dewi daripada satu insiden ketika mereka berada di Madinah. Walau bagaimanapun, cinta Reyhan itu terhalang apabila Dewi mempunyai kekasih bernama Adam. Dalam masa yang sama, seorang gadis bernama Aliyah pula menaruh hati kepada Reyhan.

programme.title: My Stupid Boss
programme.desc: Seorang perempuan indonesia datang ke kuala lumpur mengikut suaminya. Setelah berada di kuala lumpur dia berhasrat untuk bekerja di syarikat milik rakan suaminya. Majikannya itu merupakan seorang yang memiliki sikap dan perangai yang membuatnya sentiasa berada dalam keadaan serba salah dan tertekan. Sikap majikannya yang tidak mahu membayar hutang, menuduhnya mengambil wang syarikat dan tidak membayar gaji menyebabkan dia nekad untuk berhenti kerja. Namun kisah berakhir apabila dia bersetuju untuk bekerja semula apabila majikannya memintanya menguruskan kerja-kerja kebajikan membaiki rumah anak yatim.

programme.title: Taste of Life (T) Ep10831084
programme.desc: Chu-Tsai,Chao and his wife Chin-hsiu,Li have five children. Devoted all his life into developing soy sauce products, Chu-Tsai very much hopes that one of his kids can follow his footsteps and take over his business, but he also respects their own passions and aspirations. Because of their father’s invention dream, the Chao brothers’ lives are about to change… Chin-Pang,Chou used to be Chin-Hsiu’s lover, and has been Chu-Tsai’s long-time business rival. Seeing Chu-Tsai not only successfully keep the patents of soy sauce products, but also has all the support and assistance from his children, Chin-Pang, filled with bitterness, has been crushing and attacking Chu-Tsai in every way. Hsin-Ta, Chu-Tsai’s eldest son, couldn’t bear to see his father suffer, so he quit his job to take over the family business. To everyone’s surprise, Chu-Tsai discovers that Hsin-Ta is actually Chin-Pang’s son! Finding out that the enemy is actually his biological father devastated Hsin-Ta, and this also drives a wedge between Chin-pang and his son Hsiao-Ming, as he feels threatened. Chu-tsai’s second son Ying-kai has always set his goal to reach the top of his career. Vacillating between Mei-mei and Ying-hui, Ying-kai also finds himself caught in between the feud of two families; however, this opens new business opportunities for him. On the other hand, Hsin-ta fulfills Chu-tsai’s dream; but he is more confused than ever about family love and romance love… All he knows is that with the family’s support, his determination and conviction, he can build a future of his own!

programme.desc: <Stylish Man – The Chef> is co-hosted by the Golden Bell Awards winner Sam Tseng, Bernice Tsai and Genie Chuo, together with two professional chefs, A-Chi and James. There are two main themes for the program, which are “Big Stars Come to Cook” and “Five-Star Cooking Show”. <Stylish Man – The Chef> containing not only the bomb of laughter, but the audience can also gain practical cooking knowledge throughout the program.

programme.title: New Taiwan Go (M) Ep2640
programme.desc: Depth analysis of the day breaking news headlines to restore the truth inside

programme.title: iWalker-Moving Kitchen (M)(repeat) Ep3
programme.desc: Tuesday "iWalker" has been upgraded and changed the name into "iWalker-Moving Kitchen". James and the pretty chef, Rachel will move to different province with the mobile kitchen which costs more than 2 million NTD, and introduce to the audience the unique taste of the province.

programme.title: Taste of Life (T) Ep10851086
programme.desc: Chu-Tsai,Chao and his wife Chin-hsiu,Li have five children. Devoted all his life into developing soy sauce products, Chu-Tsai very much hopes that one of his kids can follow his footsteps and take over his business, but he also respects their own passions and aspirations. Because of their father’s invention dream, the Chao brothers’ lives are about to change… Chin-Pang,Chou used to be Chin-Hsiu’s lover, and has been Chu-Tsai’s long-time business rival. Seeing Chu-Tsai not only successfully keep the patents of soy sauce products, but also has all the support and assistance from his children, Chin-Pang, filled with bitterness, has been crushing and attacking Chu-Tsai in every way. Hsin-Ta, Chu-Tsai’s eldest son, couldn’t bear to see his father suffer, so he quit his job to take over the family business. To everyone’s surprise, Chu-Tsai discovers that Hsin-Ta is actually Chin-Pang’s son! Finding out that the enemy is actually his biological father devastated Hsin-Ta, and this also drives a wedge between Chin-pang and his son Hsiao-Ming, as he feels threatened. Chu-tsai’s second son Ying-kai has always set his goal to reach the top of his career. Vacillating between Mei-mei and Ying-hui, Ying-kai also finds himself caught in between the feud of two families; however, this opens new business opportunities for him. On the other hand, Hsin-ta fulfills Chu-tsai’s dream; but he is more confused than ever about family love and romance love… All he knows is that with the family’s support, his determination and conviction, he can build a future of his own!

programme.title: The Tradition Story of Taiwan (T) Ep46194620
programme.desc: The Tradition Story of Taiwan presents a series of tales and folktales in Taiwan that have been pass down from one generation to another generation

programme.desc: Different in age, generation, and hosting style, these three hosts not only can sing, act, dance, and imitate, but are also skilled in cross-talk! With this unique combination, we hope to attract viewers of all ages and spark great entertainment.

programme.title: iWalker-West Eyes to the East (M) (Repeat) Ep16
programme.desc: "iWalker - West Eyes to the East" followed the host, Rifat who is a foreigner that traveled abroad, leading the audience to experience Taiwan, which has never been seen before.

programme.title: Infernal Affairs II
programme.desc: This silver screen epic, a prequel to Infernal Affairs, hit the astonishing $16.8 million box office mark one week after its premiere. The second installment of the Infernal Affairs trilogy brings audiences with ultimate suspense and high quality action scenes! Turning into a Chinese version of the popular Godfather series, Infernal Affairs II offers its viewers an even tighter plot with a brilliant cast led by Edison Chen, Shawn Yue, Carina Lau, Eric Tsang, Anthony Wong, and Francis Ng to supply top entertainment that has rarely been seen in modern Hong Kong cinema. A legend is born at the best of times. From the multiple award-winning team behind the mind-blowing blockbuster, the secrets are finally revealed in this most anticipating prequel: What drove police superintendent Wong (Anthony Wong) and crime boss Sam (Eric Tsang) against one another? How did two struggling moles Yan (Shawn Yue) and Ming (Edison Chen) begin their parallel fates? The keys lie in the hands of three: Sam's wife Mary (Carina Lau), ruthless kingpin Hau (Francis Ng), and righteous cop Luk (Hu Jun). The infernal gates are open to the worst of times...

programme.title: Love After Love
programme.desc: Directed by Ann Hui, the movie is adapted from Eileen Chang’s first short story. Set in 1930s, Wei Long travels to Hong Kong from Shanghai to pursue her education. Struggling financially, she asks her aunt to help pay for tuition but ends up being her aunt’s puppet to lure rich men. When Wei Long falls for playboy, George, she sinks into a life of depravity.

programme.title: Legendary Amazons
programme.desc: Produced by Jackie Chan, this is the story about the fabled Yang family of female generals in feudal China. Yang Zong Bao, the last man standing in the Yang family, dies in a battle when defending the Song Dynasty from invaders. Zong Bao’s wife Mu Gui Ying steps up to lead other widows of the Yang’s into battle to continue their husband’s legacy.

programme.title: The Way We Are
programme.desc: Set in Tin Shui Wai, a marginalised satellite town, Kwai is a middle-aged widow who works hard in a neighbourhood supermarket to support herself and her son. They lead a mundane but fulfilling life. When an elderly woman who lives alone moved in to Tin Shui Wai, Kwai strikes up a friendship with her and helps her ease into a new life.

programme.title: The Eagle Shooting Heroes
programme.desc: Executive produced by Wong Kar Wai, “The Eagle Shooting Heroes” is loosely based on Louis Cha’s classics. Whilst mistaken identity and rampant gender confusion are on the menu, Sammo Hung’s action direction and the incredible all-star casts also keep the laughs and thrills coming in this Hong Kong-style crazy comedy.

programme.title: Still Human
programme.desc: Evelyn, a Filipino domestic helper, moves to Hong Kong to work for Cheong Wing, a divorcee paralyzed in a construction accident. Becoming unlikely friends, the two discover shared humanity that helps them face life’s mounting hardships.

programme.title: Shaolin Kung Fu Kids
programme.desc: Bo is separated from other Shaolin disciples when they are on the way to perform. He meets a family from Hong Kong and gets help from them. When this family faces difficulties, Bo uses his kung fu to help them solve those problems.

programme.title: The Empty Hands
programme.desc: Mari Hirakawa inherits her father’s dojo after his death but wants to sell it as she does not want to run the karate practice. For her plan to succeed, she has to take on a bet with his father’s ex-student and compete in a martial arts competition that will change her life.

programme.title: Queen of Triads
programme.desc: An innocent young girl named Zuo Lan attempts to commit suicide after she was betrayed by her boyfriend. However, she is saved by a gangster boss called Zui Ge. In order to exact her revenge, Zuo Lan joins force with Zui Ge and becomes a top mobster…

programme.title: Bleeding Steel
programme.desc: A Hong Kong police inspector, Lin Dong, had to protect an important witness in his mission thirteen years ago. This not only forced him to be separated from his daughter, but also got him involved in a conspiracy spanning more than a decade.

programme.title: Trivisa
programme.desc: In the beginning of 1997, Hong Kong's three notorious thieves who have never met one another before appear in the same restaurant. This leads to a rumour that they are joining forces to pull off something big before the Handover, though this is not something that any of them is aware of.

programme.title: All's Well End's Well 2011
programme.desc: Popular make-up artist Sammy is hired as the CEO of a cosmetics company with all women staff. As he is clueless with women, he invites Arnold, a fellow make-up artist, to join and help him. Though Arnold might appear to be a woman's magnet, his heart still lingers with his first love, Mona.

programme.title: Legend of the Demon Cat
programme.desc: Adapted from a Japanese fantasy novel, a demon cat appears and breaks the peace of Chang'an city, causing a series of mysterious events. A poet and a Japanese monk band together to follow the trails left by the cat, leading them to discover a buried secret.

programme.title: Echoes of the Rainbow
programme.desc: Set in Hong Kong in the 1960s, the story revolves around the family of a hardworking shoemaker Mr Law, with his happy-go-lucky wife and two sons – a talented elder son and an eight-year-old eccentric younger son. While their lives are not always smooth-sailing, the family sticks together and support one another through thick and thin.

programme.title: Hello Mr. Billionaire
programme.desc: An incompetent soccer goalkeeper for a minor league suddenly inherits thirty billion yuan in this mind-boggling comedy. In order to get the full amount, he must first spend one billion yuan on himself in a month without telling anyone about the task, and is also not allowed to own any assets at the end of it.

programme.title: Needing You
programme.desc: Office politics and love between co-workers complicates the lives of two computer-company employees in this romantic comedy starring Andy Lau and Sammi Cheng.

programme.title: Defying Chase
programme.desc: A stunt man is inadvertently caught in a criminal operation involving culture relics hustling, and has to fight for himself in a series of dangerous adventures.

programme.title: Napping Kid
programme.desc: Xiao Ru’s financial analysis for a bank client was stolen online. A ransom has to be paid within three days or else the document would be disclosed. To protect the client’s data, the company brings in the police to investigate. In the meantime, an analyst disappears and the Technical Director resigns. Is there a bigger crisis lurking behind?

programme.title: New Police Story
programme.desc: Senior Inspector Wing is an elite in the police force but has been drowning his guilt in booze after his entire team was killed by the “Gang of Five” in a mission. A year later, a young rookie detective with a complicated background is assigned to partner Wing and manages to inspire him into action, as Wing vows to take down the gang.

programme.title: My Alien Girlfriend
programme.desc: When Angela arrives from another planet in search of her brother, fate has her unexpectedly meet handsome veterinarian Tian Yi, who risks himself to save her every time she gets into trouble. Though she is no believer of love, his actions eventually move her…

programme.title: A Wedding Invitation
programme.desc: A boy’s marriage proposal was rejected by the girl and the lovers separated. Nonetheless, they agree on a break-up contract stating that if both are single in five years they will get married. Can they finally be together?

programme.title: Heroic Duo
programme.desc: Police officer Ken needs help to solve a grisly crime that the offender has no recollection of committing. Ken seeks out Jack, a former psychologist who is now imprisoned. Forming an uneasy truce, this unconventional duo sets out to find the man responsible. It is at this time that Ken falls into a trap set up by Jack…

programme.title: Missbehavior
programme.desc: A group of friends who are formerly close but now somewhat estranged, unite to help one of their own who is in trouble at work. In this hilarious comedy, the friends must find a replacement bottle of breast milk before the end of the day as chaos breaks out!

programme.title: Kung Fu Dunk
programme.desc: Shi Jie grew up in a martial arts school and possesses an extraordinary shooting skill. Street hustler Chen Li sees his talent and arranges for him to join a university basketball team. With his kung fu dunking skill, Shi Jie manages to win all college basketball matches, bringing him wealth and also strengthening his relationship with Chen Li.

programme.title: PTU
programme.desc: When OCTB (Organized Crime And Triad Bureau) officer, Sergeant Lo Sa, loses his police revolver to four triad young thugs, he seeks help from Sergeant Mike Ho of the PTU (Police Tactical Unit) to find his lost revolver. Ho and his patrolling PTU team has until dawn to recover the gun and clean up the mess.

programme.title: I Still Remember
programme.desc: Chi is a property agent who leads an aimless and unfulfilling life until he reunites with his P.E. teacher, Wong, from primary school. Despite his illness, Wong insists on keeping his promise of completing a 10K marathon to his late wife. Inspired by Wong, Chi brings himself to his feet and finds the courage to cheer himself on!

programme.title: Only Cloud Knows
programme.desc: This romantic drama is based on the story of a real-life couple. It follows a grieving husband as he journeys to places of significance to his beloved dead wife across their New Zealand homeland.

programme.title: Leio
programme.desc: An ex-singer Kao returns to his hometown for a funeral and takes part in a water drilling contest to save his drought-stricken hometown, as well as to win a million dollar cash prize. However, what Kao and other contestants do not realize is that there is a fierce and deadly beast lurking underground who wants to eat them all!

programme.title: Kill Mobile
programme.desc: Seven friends get together and decide to play a game where they must share all the messages, calls and app notifications on each other's cell phones. Hilarity and drama follows as everyone's secrets are unveiled throughout the evening, and the seven friends find themselves more like strangers to each other than ever before!

programme.title: The White Storm 2: Drug Lords
programme.desc: In this epic action-thriller starring Andy Lau and Louis Koo, the two award-winning best actors star on opposing sides of a drug war. As a bounty of $100 million Hong Kong dollars is made to hunt down the biggest drug dealer in the city, Hong Kong becomes the battleground for the fight between good and evil.

programme.title: Acting Out of Love
programme.desc: Wei Hung Jen is a struggling actor who gets fired but finds a job behind the scene. Hui Hsin, the associate producer, must write a script for a love story so as to get a reference letter to study scriptwriting overseas. As Jen falls for Hui, he invites her out on a date as a research for her script and they start acting out of love.

programme.title: The Bodyguard
programme.desc: A retired bodyguard who is suffering from early stages of dementia befriends a young girl whose life is threatened when her father falls in with the international crime world. The girl disappeared one day, and the bodyguard vows to save the life of his young friend.

programme.title: Knockout
programme.desc: A former boxing champion and convict who has just been released from prison discovers that his wife has died and he is now a single parent. The situation is made worse with his daughter’s diagnosis of leukaemia. In order to encourage his daughter and fulfil his promise of never giving up, he re-enters the boxing ring.

programme.title: The Imperial Swordsman
programme.desc: Fu is a government officer heading home after being charged with falsifying reports. En route, he encounters & recruits a skilled swordsman as a bodyguard. They then meet a fleeing bride and her maid who asked to join them for protection. When the group reach a ruined temple however, a gang of assassins appear and attack them…

programme.title: The Yellow Muffler
programme.desc: Japanese director Inoue Umetsugu takes on the glitzy world of nightclub performers in The Yellow Muffler. The film depicts the struggle of two singing sisters, Ching-ping (Irene Chen I-ling) and Pai-hung (Betty Ting Pei) and ends when they are cast in a new movie.

programme.title: The Avenging Eagle
programme.desc: Chik, one of the assassins of the Iron Boat Clan, decides to leave the clan when a kind family saved him. When pursued by the clan, a swordsman whose wife was killed by him saved his life. They decide to jointly take revenge on the clan.

programme.title: Boxer Rebellion
programme.desc: The Empress Dowager Cixi believes the Boxers’ claim that they have developed a kung fu that makes them impervious to weapons, thus declaring war against the alliances of eight foreign nations. The lack of weapons and good leadership in the Ching government allows the Eight Nation Alliances to take down Beijing.

programme.title: Five Tough Guys
programme.desc: A titular gang of misfits come together to protect a patriotic general from a scheming usurper. To this end, the unlikely heroes act as the general’s escorts on a dangerous journey to a distant British consulate, beset by enemies and sinister Japanese interference along the way.

programme.title: Sons Of Good Earth
programme.desc: This is an epic tale set during the time of the Sino-Japanese war. A painter Yu saves a young girl, Lotus, who is being sold to a brothel. They fall in love, get married and settled in to a peaceful life. However, their life is soon shattered by the Japanese invasion and the brutal regime that follows.

programme.title: The Supreme Swordsman
programme.desc: After beating several famous swordsmen, Chin Wu-hsin (Pai Piao) of the Mo Shan clan challenges Supreme Swordsman (Wang Jung) to a duel, hoping to win his title, and is beaten and humiliated. The winner taunts him to find a Supreme Sword made by Old Eagle, a famous sword-maker (Ku Feng). When his offer to buy a sword from Old Eagle, is turned down, he challenges Old Eagle to a duel, and snatches his sword in a foul play. Old Eagle's own son Shih Yen-peh (Derek Yee) vows to avenge for his father...

programme.title: Torrent Of Desire
programme.desc: Rich playboy David is a drunk until he falls in love with a fashion model Dan Feng and marries her. David's sister Mona is in love with his best friend Han Ming, who rejected her as he secretly loves Dan Feng as well. Out of jealousy and hatred, Mona lies to David about a fake affair between Han Ming and Dan Feng...

programme.title: Men From The Gutter
programme.desc: Two very different cops are out to capture a local drug boss. In this sizzling crime thriller, the two cops go about doing their jobs differently - one does everything to the letter of the law and the other just doing whatever it takes to solve crime.

programme.title: Call of the Sea
programme.desc: A young fisherman, Chin Hu is in love with his childhood friend Hsiao Yu. However, the only son of a town bully lusts after Hsiao Yu’s beauty and tries all possible ways to approach her. Chin Hu protects another woman from the bully one day, leading Hsiao Yu to misunderstand him and suspect that they are having an affair...

programme.title: Portrait In Crystal
programme.desc: Tragic deaths in the underworld cause leader "Yama" (Teng Wei-hao) to suspect a portrait in crystal with mysterious powers. He sends Hen Pan (Chen Hung) and Pai Pan (Hung Hsin-nan) to interrogate its creator, martial artist Lung Fei (Pai Piao)...

programme.title: Operation Lipstick
programme.desc: A professor’s assistant stole a micro-film storing the secret of a newly invented nuclear reactor and sells it to a crime syndicate. However, the micro-film accidentally falls into the hands of a nightclub dancer and a thief in the process, leading to them being relentlessly pursued by the crime syndicate to retrieve the micro-film.

programme.title: Love Parade
programme.desc: Fashion designer Shi asks his friend Mui to comment on his new design but is angered by her criticism. When Mui asks him to design a gown for her to attend a gala event, Shi takes revenge by making a clown costume instead. Seeing Mui’s embarrassment, Shi feels guilty and apologizes to her, before they fall in love…

programme.title: The Hidden Power Of Dragon Sabre
programme.desc: Defeated villain Sung Ching Shu returns and starts a reign of terror, trapping a beautiful Mongolian Princess and mastering the "yin and yang combination" to become almost invincible. Only two swords held by two great swordsmen can stand in his way!

programme.title: Whose Baby is in the Classroom?
programme.desc: Chen, a male teacher in an all girls’ high school, is stuck with a baby that isn’t his and must take care of it. As he lives on the school grounds, the baby is a source of constant distraction and worry! Luckily, his class warms to the baby and helps him take care of it while he works his charm on Li Ching, an uptight teacher in the same school.

programme.title: The Dragon Creek
programme.desc: This wuxia murder mystery film talks about a young girl whose father was ruthlessly murdered during China's early republican era. She has a list of villains who have been plotting against her father and together with her elder brother, the young girl sets out on a journey to hunt down the secret serial killer.

programme.title: Tales of Larceny
programme.desc: Connecting all the antics of bosses, monks, beggars, and thieves is the slippery and sinuous efforts of three pickpockets so adept at their chosen skill that they can even trick three beauties of their underwear without missing a step.

programme.title: The Singing Killer
programme.desc: Chiang Yi is blackmailed into a jewelry heist by his former boss, who threatens to expose his shady past. Complications arise when he discovers his first love works at the store.

programme.title: We Love Millionaires
programme.desc: In this romantic comedy, three beautiful Hong Kong salesgirls travel to Osaka in Japan to pursue their dreams of marrying a rich man. They masquerade as high society debutantes and make their way to a posh resort to meet and woo millionaires (or fake ones!).

programme.title: The Kid With A Tattoo
programme.desc: Young Bao Tong witnesses the brutal murder of his kung fu master by a vicious villain. A large eagle tattoo on Bao’s chest was spotted by the killer as he escapes. Can Bao escape from the killer?

programme.title: The Voyage of Emperor Chien Lung
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung continues his incognito voyage to southern China. Accompanied by the minister and the imperial scholar, they have many amusing encounters in Yangzhou.

programme.title: Police Force
programme.desc: A man joins the Hong Kong police force to track down a murderer who has killed his friend in a robbery. While he struggles to reconcile his law defending police duty with his desire for vengeance, he also has a new-found respect for the law.

programme.title: Asia-pol
programme.desc: Asiapol agent Yang Ming Xuan trails a shipment of contraband gold being delivered to gang leader, George Eaton. He enlists the help of a Chinese woman who is trying to avenge her sister and narrowly escapes several deadly traps as he closes in on Eaton's location. This spy film is loosely inspired by the James Bond movies.

programme.title: Trilogy Of Swordsmanship
programme.desc: A kung fu anthology film consisting of three stories: a man embarrasses himself while trying to prove his worth to the father of the woman he loves; a courtesan in love with a general will need to deliver a notorious bandit in exchange for him not being executed; and a group of bandits forms a plan to rescue a new friend from being executed.

programme.title: Return Of The Dead
programme.desc: A long-awaited horror sequel after Enchanted Shadow, this is about three asylum inmates telling their stories. In story one, a husband and wife discover they should be careful what they wish for. A naked female ghost seeks revenge from her watery grave in story two, and a dead prostitute returns as a ghost in the last tale.

programme.title: Come Drink with Me
programme.desc: The brother of the mystery swordswoman "Golden Swallow” is kidnapped. She joins forces with a beggar “Drunken Cat” who is skilled in martial arts to free her brother from a Buddhist monastery run by a corrupt abbot. The film was selected as Hong Kong’s entry for the Best Foreign Language Film at the 39th Academy Awards.

programme.title: The Young Avenger
programme.desc: Liu seeks out Li to avenge his brother’s death and loses an arm in the fight, vowing revenge ten years later. Li dies after asking his sister to send his daughter Bao Zhu to learn the Dragon Sword skill to avenge his death. Bao Zhu grows up to become a skilled swordswoman and meets Liu for the planned duel with her cousin Chen. Can she defeat Liu?

programme.title: Mr. Funnybone Strikes Again
programme.desc: In this hilarious sequel, Mr Big Potato opens an old-fashioned Chinese clinic, but his traditional methods are rejected by the sceptics of modern Hong Kong. Enter his buddy Mr Funny bone to rescue his business!

programme.title: My Rebellious Son
programme.desc: The venerated Sun Chung made many different kinds of films for Shaw Brothers, including popular and renowned satirical comedies, contemporary action dramas, and magnificent martial arts movies. This is one of his last of the latter for the studio, so he wanted to have fun... and let the audience share it. Toward that end he cast international favorite Alexander Fu Sheng as the title character who keeps testing the patience (and kung-fu skills) of his father, a small town bonesetter and herbal healer played by award-winning character actor Ku Feng. But when a local dignitary not only smuggles drugs but plans to give a Chinese treasure away to evil outsiders, the father and son unite to take on foreign fighters and even Japanese ninja in a non-stop display of comic action prowess.

programme.title: The Big Sting
programme.desc: Three buddies find a rare artifact known as the Double-Faced God but are poisoned by Lady Wu who steals the treasure from them. Before they die, they get their wives to promise to train their children to take back what is rightfully theirs. These kids grow up to exact a vengeance that turns out to be more hilarious than horrific in this comedy.

programme.title: Two Champions of Shaolin
programme.desc: Set in the Qing Dynasty, the Shaolin clan wants to overthrow Qing and restore the Ming Dynasty, while the Wudang clan is backed by the Qing government. The two renowned clans eventually set themselves up against each other, and a series of vicious fighting has just begun…

programme.title: Dawn will Come
programme.desc: Liang Cai drugged the beautiful Qiu Rong and raped her, but promised to marry her after getting his parent’s consent. Since then, there is no news of his proposal and Qiu Rong confronts Liang Cai when she finds herself pregnant. This is when she discovers that he has already married a rich noble girl and even plans to kill her…

programme.title: Vengeance
programme.desc: Yu Lou is betrayed by his wife, and eventually killed by her lover, Fung, who is the boss of a martial arts school. Yu Lou’s brother Xiao Lou knows about his tragic death and is determined to take revenge on Fung and his sister-in-law.

programme.title: The Tiger and the Widow
programme.desc: The Liu Chia-liang trained Hui Ying-hung was considered the top action martial arts female star in the 1980s. It is her martial arts abilities that Michelle Yeoh tries to emulate. In The Tiger and the Widow, Hui Ying-hung is somehow mixed up in a salt smuggling ring that stinks of missing persons and rotten dilemmas.

programme.title: The Treasure Hunters
programme.desc: Fans of the international star Alexander Fu Sheng were aghast. Their idol had broken both his legs and was recuperating. Everyone wondered: would he be able to return to the action comedies for which he was so famous? This movie was the answer, and it left no doubt that he had made a full recovery. Liu Chia-yung, brother of preeminent martial arts moviemaker Liu Chia-liang, was famous in his own right for kung-fu comedies, and he out-did himself with this one. Imagine Bob Hope and Bing Crosby with the skills of Jet Li and Jackie Chan, and you’ve got an idea of the fun and fury inherent in this delightful tale of two con men vying for a horde of hidden gold. Add to the mix a Shaolin monk (played by "Master Killer" Gordon Liu Chia-hui), a powerfully brutal villain (Wang Lung-wei), and his equally dangerous mute sister (future director Yang Tsing-tsing), and you’ve got one of the most internationally loved kung-fu capers ever made.

programme.title: Irumbuthirai
programme.desc: Tamil Action Movie, Starring, Vishal, Samantha Akkineni, Arjun Sarja, Sreeja Ravi & others

programme.title: Kamali From Nadukaveri
programme.desc: Tamil Film, Starring, Anandhi, Rohit Saraf, Prathap Pothen, Imman Annachi & Others

The last remaining deep pools are inhabited by hippos – hundreds squashed together in the only water deep enough to submerge them. As tempers flare and skirmishes break out, it’s a dangerous place for baby hippos, dwarfed by the three-tonne adults.

programme.title: Noddy Toyland Detective Ep41
programme.desc: The Case Of The Missing Players - It's time for the Toyland football match but the game can't go ahead until Noddy finds the missing players. Noddy discovers that someone misdirected Pat Pat and Deltoid so that they'd miss the match. Noddy finds the missing players and reunites everyone at the real football pitch but then Hoof disappears. Noddy discovers that Hoof misdirected the others because he wanted to be the best player. Hoof learns that football is a team sport where all the team members need to work together to make it the best game ever. Well done Noddy!

programme.title: Noddy Toyland Detective Ep42
programme.desc: The Case Of The Changed Basketball Hoop - Noddy's about to play a game of basketball with Big Ears and Deltoid when he realizes that the hoop has been fiddled with. Who could've done that and why? Noddy's investigation leads him to Fuse, who explains that he just wanted to help the toys that weren't as skilled as him. Everyone practises and realises that the best way to improve at sport is to keep practising. Well done Noddy.

programme.title: Noddy Toyland Detective Ep43
programme.desc: The Case Of The Ruined Crops - Farmer Tom is confused and upset when he finds all his trees and corn knocked over. Noddy decides to investigate: who spoiled Farmer Tom's crops? He soon discovers lots of strange heavy bags scattered all over the farm. Whose are they? Where did they come from? And what could they possibly have to do with Smartysaurus's new hot air balloon?

programme.title: 2023 Gran Premio Michelin de la República Argentina Highlights
programme.desc: Highlights - MotoGP ™ returned to Argentina in 2014 after a long 15-year break, with the Termas de Rio Hondo circuit in the northern province of Santiago del Estero becoming the host venue for the Gran Premio de la Republica Argentina - a race that had previously been held in Buenos Aires. Indeed, the first ever Argentinean Grand Prix took place in 1961 close to Argentina’s capital, and was the first time that a GP had been run outside Europe. In the modern era Termas de Rio Hondo continues the legacy of motorcycle racing in Argentina. The annual visit to the South American country creates a festival atmosphere, providing a spectacular show on and off track.
